                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18131027-95-victim991 t18131027-95-viclabel566"></join>, Oxford-street. On the 19th of October, the prisoner came into the shop, and ordered candles to the amount of sixteen shillings and nine-pence, to be sent to No. 26, Sackville-street, with change of a two-pound note. I gave 
               <persName id="t18131027-95-person994">
                  Daniel 
                  Law
               <interp inst="t18131027-95-person994" type="surname" value="Law"></interp>
